description: DYMO 1812570 LabelManager Wireless Plug N Play Label Maker. No software to install. Just plug into PC or Mac, and create great-looking, durable labels. Wireless lets you share with everyone on your network. Create custom labels with using fonts and graphics on your PC or Mac. Print graphics, barcodes and logos in professional-quality 300 dpi resolution. Uses easy-peel, split-back D1 tape (1/4-, 3/8-, or 1/2-inch sizes). Thermal printing creates labels with no ink or toner. Automatic label cutter makes multi-label printing effortless. 1 year limited warranty. Includes rechargeable battery pack, USB power adapter, USB cable, and 1-inch D1 starter label cassette black on white.
title: DYMO 1812570 LabelManager Wireless Plug N Play Label Maker
